se I was dumb and didn't put any into my Skald when I made him (it was like the first week the game came out and I didn't research anything)... <p><HR><BR><IMG SRC="http://home.satx.rr.com/skratch/sig2.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/upfalcon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PFalcon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Member</span><br>  Posts: 44<br> <font color=#ff0000>(6/19/02 10:43:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=197.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.dallasbest.net/honourbound/images/pf.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How does this look</span><hr size=1> I like 10 Con 15 Charisma<br><br>in the endgame those 10 con mean more than 10 in str, and 15 charisma is a must for more damage from spells. <p><p><img border="0" src="http://www.dallasbest.net/honourbound/images/acapella_sig.jpg"</p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ugisborne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gisborne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#ff0000>(6/19/02 11:10:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=197.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How does this look</span><hr size=1> Why is cha a must for spell damage but str isn't for weapon damage when 3/4 of our damage is from melee?<br><br>10 str/con/cha.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uvahn666.showPublicProfile?language=EN>vahn666</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="h